{"tid":1696873,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"文功武略 - 我終於諗到抗爭必勝打法","createTime":"2019-11-06T12:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:49:30.000Z","uid":108757,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"94dfbbe36105a3d27c538d2b7cb635541944eb5e","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"先講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武略 - 遊行、集會、所有街頭活動</span></span><br />\n由六月開始，已經好多人指出咗活動嘅核心問題︰<span style=\"color: red;\">「無明確目標」</span><br />\n有目標嘅活動，多數成功，例612、71、823 人鏈、115 V煞......，所以我地以後所有活動都要有目標，宜家個樽頸就係個目標係乜？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係「攬炒」！</span></span><br />\n<strong>玩法︰</strong>由今日開始，每個活動除本身主題之外(例如聲援新彊維吾爾人、人權民主法......)，<span style=\"color: red;\">另一個主要目標就係「攬炒」</span>。<br />\n<strong>勝利條件︰</strong>只要活動期間，附近商場、店舖已經差唔多<span style=\"color: red;\">落晒閘</span>，就為之勝利。之後就應該<span style=\"color: red;\">立即轉場</span>，令到第二個地方嘅商場、店舖都落閘。之後再轉場，去第三個地方，如此類推。轉到入夜，準時返屋企。<br />\n<strong>理念︰</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「攬炒」只係手段，最終目的係「全民勇武」</span>。當每個星期六日全九龍都落晒閘，商家好快頂唔住，炒人、執笠、撤資，當好多人無工開，就自然會上街問政府拎錢！「攬炒」成功之時，就係「全民勇武」之時。當前嘅「落閘大行動」係直接導致「攬炒」嘅手段，所以記住<span style=\"color: red;\">「落閘」之時，就係轉場之時</span>！所有活動當綠曱甴係Grad din毒撚就得，唔洗理佢地！佢叫我地走，就轉場！<br />\n<br />\n再講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文功 - 區議會選舉</span></span><br />\n區選最大問題係種票，宜家禁咗選民查冊，更加唔知對家會種到咩地步。但係我已經諗到必勝方法︰<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「推高真投票率」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08n0wEc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08n0wEc.png&h=e9724dcb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>玩法︰</strong>區選總選民人數有413萬，即係所有選區加埋最多會有413萬票，即係投票率最多係100%。種票意思係「無呢個人，但有呢張票」。大家計下數<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">投票率</span> = <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">真投票率</span> + <span style=\"color: red;\">種票率</span><br />\n假設<span style=\"color: red;\">種票率係10%</span>，只要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">真投票率有91%</span>，咁<span style=\"color: gold;\">投票率就等於101%</span>????<br />\n點解會有票係多咗？唔止香港，全世界都知啲票有問題啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">只要多咗一票，政府仆街死都唔掂</span>！<br />\n我地要做嘅係推高真投票率，<span style=\"color: red;\">真投票率愈高，種票率愈低</span>。<br />\n<strong>理念︰</strong>要抗爭成功，不論制度內外，所有方法都要試！選舉係0成本嘅抗爭方法，只要解決種票問題就好大機會嬴。而過去嘅選舉，投票率(計埋種票率)都只係40幾%，即係有大半班人無投票！<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要做嘅係盡量推、叫、拉佢地出去投票</span>，無論係投咩票都好，推高投票率會令選舉更加公平！保皇黨快啲種多啲票啦喂！<span style=\"color: red;\">種得少佢地輸硬，種得多過咗100%，就即刻仆街死</span>！完全係極低成本抗爭方法。唔好話投票率90%以上係無可能，抗爭到宜家香港人已經多次將係可能變成可能，只要落手落腳做，香港人無野做唔到！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唯一漏洞就係選管會數據做假，如果係咁，所有制度都變成垃圾，香港人應該全民勇武，唔洗再有任何包袱同冀望。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">MON PO 曱甴可以收皮，你地無機會嬴！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDoi2SO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDoi2SO.gif&h=2279f302&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yu6sjK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yu6sjK.gif&h=6f8514f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42c798deb2b94906ac90df2b1479c33c62e1d9dd","tid":1696873,"uid":239203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"要加快經濟攬炒<br />\n<br />\n其實只要我地唔割繼續堅持落去就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2218d18d9bcc759bd6ef078a4acf28cbdf3a0fb","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kd6wDvp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKd6wDvp.gif&h=681211c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cc2b4a3c097fe82c2c5705b42818dcf2c98b74f","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"種多啲票啦，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c13a264c9d4019968f821f640cb78b84619cbde","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7e1d692190ba0c6839726113904c9d22526732","tid":1696873,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"區議會選民報名一早deadline左<br />\n而家點掙扎都推高唔到投票率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈多人無申請做選民 種票空間就愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f154c71d4e3e784bb368ff1410c5111dc11e8c5","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c7e1d692190ba0c6839726113904c9d22526732","tid":1696873,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"區議會選民報名一早deadline左<br />\n而家點掙扎都推高唔到投票率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈多人無申請做選民 種票空間就愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"手足要清醒啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票率淨係係已登記選民 = 413萬<br />\n投票率 = 投票人數 / 413萬<br />\n<br />\n無登記係唔計的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df29281e4adddc0fbd85671134d78d044efa4f8","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdeb0578aad45ab16c72907269e92462fcf59cc","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHb1gmK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHb1gmK.gif&h=77c3d080&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d52dde71b03e1e469747b71a830c468f79f1dc5d","tid":1696873,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"明知一早抗爭係最直接影響罷工 都話