id":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c3f08848798d5ccb4346cf07ab2a3a8e933c45a","tid":1696873,"uid":72863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"必勝方法係每個人出多少少力<br />\n話說我老豆本身中立，俾我瘋狂開住32台吸收真實新聞變成淺黃，唔知邊位手足今日同我老豆講連登先最真！<br />\n搞到我老豆追撚住我叫佢幫下載，手足你好野<br />\n<br />\n多謝你感染佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"每個人做盡一百分，先係各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6a024d0690a5eb6493177c65390721bcc7afcb","tid":1696873,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"f55d6c25aa7897beb0dc5d1328e69449a17eee62","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cbf57043c4870c3e13b153da667e23480b201a","tid":1696873,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"想參加罷工，但又驚冇左份工？輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要人！制更制！日日炒經濟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696258</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa06d9f28fd4f49be5d143d80ff20540dd897f69","tid":1696873,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"抗爭是建設社會，不是破壞社會。我們要將這落後思想摒棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8904e8ad27e801a33165e7e027c1430c3336f787","tid":1696873,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fabab1908c6a89d79a20a38bdc474f